<td class="" style="padding:0.2em; line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle; font-size:90%;">November 16, 1952 <span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1952-11-16</span>)</span> <span class="noprint">(age&#160;56)</span><br />
