<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.famitsu.com/game/event/2005/05/18/264,1116367600,39303,0,0.html" class="external text" title="http://www.famitsu.com/game/event/2005/05/18/264,1116367600,39303,0,0.html" rel="nofollow">"【任天堂】ラウンドテーブルにて『ゼルダの伝説 Twilight Princess』の全貌が明らかに！"</a> (in Japanese). <i><a href="/wiki/Famitsu" title="Famitsu">Famitsu</a></i>. <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2005-05-18"><a href="/wiki/2005" title="2005">2005</a>-<a href="/wiki/May_18" title="May 18">05-18</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.famitsu.com/game/event/2005/05/18/264,1116367600,39303,0,0.html" class="external free" title="http://www.famitsu.com/game/event/2005/05/18/264,1116367600,39303,0,0.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.famitsu.com/game/event/2005/05/18/264,1116367600,39303,0,0.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-09-19</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=%E3%80%90%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E3%80%91%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%83%B3%E3%83%89%E3%83%86%E3%83%BC%E3%83%96%E3%83%AB%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A6%E3%80%8E%E3%82%BC%E3%83%AB%E3%83%80%E3%81%AE%E4%BC%9D%E8%AA%AC+Twilight+Princess%E3%80%8F%E3%81%AE%E5%85%A8%E8%B2%8C%E3%81%8C%E6%98%8E%E3%82%89%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AB%EF%BC%81&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2005-05-18%5D%5D&amp;rft.pub=%27%27%5B%5BFamitsu%5D%5D%27%27&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.famitsu.com%2Fgame%2Fevent%2F2005%2F05%2F18%2F264%2C1116367600%2C39303%2C0%2C0.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Shigeru_Miyamoto"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
